org.rsna.ctp.pipeline

Interface ImportService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImportService, ArchiveImportService, DicomImportService, DicomSTOWRSImportService, DirectoryImportService, HttpImportService, PollingHttpImportService

    public interface ImportService
    The interface specifying the additional methods that must be implemented by a pipeline Stage that is an ImportService.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • getNextObject

        FileObject getNextObject()
        Get the next object available for processing
        Returns:
        the next object available, or null if no object is available.

      • release

        void release(java.io.File file)
        Release a file, allowing an ImportService to clean up temporary storage if necessary. Note that other stages in the pipeline may have moved the file, so it is possible that the file will no longer exist. It is therefore important to check the existence of the file before using it.
        Parameters:
        file - the file to be released, which must be the original file supplied by the ImportService.

      • getQueueSize

        int getQueueSize()
        Get the size of the import queue.
        Returns:
        the number of objects in the import queue, or zero if the ImportService is not queued.
